ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisReappointment of WILLIAM C. ROSS of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of PPP Canada Inc., to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months or until his successor is appointed, if the appointment is made before the end of the term, effective December 23, 2008.
